body:
Comment 1 by **FishyFish55**: 
I suspected this might have been caused by something not updating properly (perhaps my
goinstalled gomatrix package). I made a new clone of the go repository and installed it,
and goinstalled gomatrix again. This particular issue seems to no longer appear, but it
still looks like it may have been a bug of some kind as regardless of what was messed up
as far as old compiled files laying around or what ever the cause may have been, those
were some nasty and confusing errors (link errors perhaps?)  that probably shouldn't
make it all the way to a compile binary output file.
